      • doInTransaction

        protected void doInTransaction(Runnable action)
        Description copied from class: JObjectContainer
        Perform the given action within a new JTransaction.

        The implementation in JObjectContainer performs action within a new read-only transaction. Note that action should be idempotent because the transaction will be retried if needed.

        Overrides:
        doInTransaction in class JObjectContainer
        Parameters:
        action - the action to perform

      • queryForObjects

        protected Iterator<? extends JObject> queryForObjects()
        Description copied from class: QueryJObjectContainer
        Query for the database objects that will be used to fill this container. Objects should be returned in the desired order; duplicates and null values will be ignored.

        A JTransaction will be open in the current thread when this method is invoked.

        Specified by:
        queryForObjects in class QueryJObjectContainer
        Returns:
        database objects
